data.title: Mrs. Alice Lee Roosevelt Longworth | 1905
data.meta_description: Mrs. Alice Lee Roosevelt Longworth (1884 – 1980) was the oldest child of Theodore Roosevelt, the 26th President of the United States. She was the only child of Roosevelt and his first wife, Alice Hathaway Lee. 1905. Source: Retrografix.com, Twitter @retrografixcom
data.text:
Mrs. Alice Lee Roosevelt Longworth (1884 – 1980) was the oldest child of Theodore Roosevelt, the 26th President of the United States. She was the only child of Roosevelt and his first wife, Alice Hathaway Lee. 1905.

Source: Retrografix.com, Twitter @retrografixcom
